ottom: 0cm\">- il campo \n<i><b>divisione</b></i> √® pari al rapporto tra il prodotto degli\nelementi della riga  e la soommatoria degli elementi della diagonale\nsecondaria.</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">- il campo <i><b>indice</b></i>\nrappresenta  l‚Äôindice di riga.</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">- il campo <i><b>n</b></i>\nindica la lunghezza della riga</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">- il  campo <i><b>vettore</b></i>\ncontiene gli elementi della riga in esame</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\"><br/>\n\n</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\"><br/>\n\n</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">Salvare i soli\nelementi inizializzati in un file binario ‚Äúoutput.bin‚Äù.</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\"><br/>\n\n</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">Esempio:</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\"><br/>\n\n</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">5</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">2 3 0 1 4</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\"><br/>\n\n</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">4 2 3 4 6</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">3 2 1 1 2</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">3 4 5 4 3</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">2 1 2 3 4</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">4 5 6 7 6</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\"><br/>\n\n</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">Matrice Ordinata:</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">3 4 4 2 6</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">1 1 3 2 2</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">5 4 3 4 3</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">2 3 2 1 4</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">6 7 4 5 6</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\"><br/>\n\n</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">Vettore Risultante</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\"><br/>\n\n</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">{28.799999,0,[ 3  4 \n4  2  6 ]}</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">{0.600000,1,[ 1  1 \n3  2  2 ]}</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">{36.000000,2,[ 5  4 \n3  4  3 ]}</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">{2.400000,3,[ 2  3 \n2  1  4 ]}</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">{252.000000,4,[ 6  7\n 4  5  6 ]}</p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">Approfondimento:\nSomma diagonale: 20, moltiplicatoria prima riga: 576, divisione:\n576/20=28,8</p>\n</body>\n</html>',0,'traccia 20230111'),(55,'vhdl/et4','vhdl',1,_binary '<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head>\n	<meta http-equiv=\"content-type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\"/>\n	<title></title>\n	<meta name=\"generator\" content=\"LibreOffice 7.3.6.2 (Linux)\"/>\n	<meta name=\"created\" content=\"2021-01-15T10:02:01.080572696\"/>\n	<meta name=\"changed\" content=\"2023-01-11T01:58:42.158096007\"/>\n	<style type=\"text/css\">\n		@page { size: 21cm 29.7cm; margin: 2cm }\n		p { line-height: 115%; margin-bottom: 0.25cm; background: transparent }\n		h1 { margin-bottom: 0.21cm; background: transparent; page-break-after: avoid }\n		h1.western { font-family: \"Liberation Sans\", sans-serif; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold }\n		h1.cjk { font-family: \"Noto Sans CJK SC\"; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold }\n		h1.ctl { font-family: \"Lohit Devanagari\"; font-size: 18pt; font-weight: bold }\n	</style>\n</head>\n<body lang=\"en-US\" link=\"#000080\" vlink=\"#800000\" dir=\"ltr\"><h1 lang=\"it-IT\" class=\"western\" align=\"center\" style=\"page-break-before: always\">\nTraccia di Architettura dei Calcolatori</h1>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\n<br/>\n\n</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\nProgettare e simulare in VHDL una macchina che possiede in ingresso:</p>\n<ul>\n	<li><p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\"><span lang=\"it-IT\"><span style=\"font-style: normal\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal\">un\n	segnale da </span></span></span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><span style=\"font-style: normal\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal\">1</span></span></span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><span style=\"font-style: normal\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal\">\n	bit </span></span></span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><span style=\"font-style: normal\"><b>d</b></span></span></p>\n	<li><p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\n	1 <b>clock</b> con periodo 10 us</p>\n	<li><p align=\"left\" style=\"line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\"><span lang=\"it-IT\"><span style=\"font-style: normal\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal\">1\n	</span></span></span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><span style=\"font-style: normal\"><b>reset</b></span></span><span lang=\"it-IT\"><span style=\"font-style: normal\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal\">	</span></span></span></p>\n</ul>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\nLa macchina presenta in uscita:</p>\n<ul>\n	<li><p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\n	un segnale <b>P</b> da 7 bit</p>\n	<li><p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\n	un segnale <b>count</b> da 4 bit</p>\n	<li><p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\n	un segnale impulsivo <b>r</b> di1 bit</p>\n</ul>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\n<br/>\n\n</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\nLa macchina dopo il <b>reset</b> comincia a campionare dati sulla\nlinea <b>d</b> su ogni fronte di salita e sul fronte di salita del\nclock.</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\n<br/>\n\n</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\nPer ogni coppia di bit ricevuta, il primo bit rappresenta un dato e\nil secondo bit un controllo.</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\nSe i due bit sono diversi il primo bit viene utilizzato per riempire\nun buffer di 8 bit.</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\n<br/>\n\n</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\nL‚Äôottavo bit dato trasmesso √® un bit di controllo parit√† pari.</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\n<br/>\n\n</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\nOgni  8 colpi di clock, se non ci sono errori,  7 bit meno\nsignificativi del buffer vengono portati in uscita sulle linee <b>P</b>\ne il segnale  <b>count</b> √® pari a 0.</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: normal; font-weight: normal; line-height: 100%; margin-bottom: 0cm\">\n<br/>\n\n</p>\n<p lang=\"it-IT\" align=\"left\" style=\"font-style: 